    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th Level you can use your Ninjutsu or Genjutsu Save DC instead of the stated DC of an explosive tool.</p><p> Explosive Tools that deal damage increase their damage by your proficiency bonus.</p><p> When using an Explosive Tool that doesn't deal damage, you can select up to 3 creatures.</p><p> A chosen creature suffers no effect from your Explosive Tool.</p><p></p>",
